ygData.messageBody:
I agree with Blitz here. I am quickly approaching planes level (got 39 and
40 this weekend...).

On veeshan, (as far as I know) Fear is always broken. We have a VERY high
Japanese population so our server population doesnt have the down time/ peak
time swings in server population you see most places.

No one in my guild has ever been to the planes (our cleric is 46, I think he
is the first to hit the level). We would like to adventure in the planes
and get planes equipment. I don't see whats wrong with that.
